    + '<em>Manager</em> — full control of this workspace, can spend credits.<br/>'
    + '<em>Editor</em> — create scans + generate content, but no billing.<br/>'
    + '<em>Viewer</em> — read-only access to scans + content.<br/>'
    + '<em>No access</em> — workspace hidden from this member.',
  members_remove: 'Remove this member from the organization.<br/><em>Their access to every workspace is revoked at the same time.</em>',

  // ── Sprint 4 — Wikipedia tab ──────────────────────────────────────────
  wikipedia_present: 'This brand has a Wikipedia page.<br/>'
    + '<em>ChatGPT cites Wikipedia ~48% of the time, so having one is a strong AI-visibility lever.</em>',
  wikipedia_absent: 'No Wikipedia page found for this brand.<br/>'
    + '<em>Notability bar is high — start by accumulating press citations rather than self-publishing.</em>',
